Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, and in particular Article 113 thereof,
Having regard to the proposal from the Commission,
Whereas Regulation (EEC) No 715/90 (1) laid down the arrangements applicable to agricultural products and to certain goods resulting from the processing of agricultural products originating in the African, Caribbean and Pacific States or the overseas  countries and territories;
